      <title>随着短缺担忧加剧，罗布斯塔咖啡创下新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/robusta-coffee-hits-fresh-record-high-as-shortage-fears-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心产量下降将加剧咖啡豆短缺，罗布斯塔咖啡在伦敦创下新纪录。阿拉比卡品种也有所上涨，可可品种也接近近期历史最高点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/robusta-coffee-hits-fresh-record-high-as-shortage-fears-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 12:15:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
